The package xdelta provides CMake targets:

    find_package(xdelta CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE xdelta::xdelta)

Or you can use the library directly:

    target_include_directories(main PRIVATE ${VCPKG_INSTALLED_DIR}/${VCPKG_TARGET_TRIPLET}/include)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE ${VCPKG_INSTALLED_DIR}/${VCPKG_TARGET_TRIPLET}/lib/xdelta.lib)

The xdelta3 command-line tool is also available:

    ${VCPKG_INSTALLED_DIR}/${VCPKG_TARGET_TRIPLET}/tools/xdelta/xdelta3.exe
